  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a medium pot over medium heat. Add mustard seeds and let them pop for about 30 seconds.",
    "Add diced onion and sauté until translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add rinsed lentils, smoked paprika, and cumin; toss to coat and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth, bring to a gentle boil, then reduce to a simmer.",
    "Add chopped kale and simmer for 10 minutes, or until lentils are tender.",
    "Stir in coconut milk and ground flaxseed; simmer for another 2 minutes until the chowder thickens and becomes fluffy.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste. Serve hot, optionally garnished with fresh herbs."
